[{"question":"Why did Jovan Belcher need a high-powered hand gun?","answer":"Well, he didn\u0027t need a -- any hand gun to kill to murder his wife and leave the poor baby as an orphan.","docId":"121203pmt","qSentId":41,"aSentId":42},{"question":"Well, I\u0027m assuming most hand guns are high powered, right?","answer":"So what you mean -- so you call it high powered handgun by which you mean a normal handgun and I don\u0027t know why he owned a handgun.","docId":"121203pmt","qSentId":51,"aSentId":52},{"question":"At what point do you say in America, enough guns, actually what we need to do is reduce the number of guns?","answer":"Right.","docId":"121203pmt","qSentId":100,"aSentId":101},{"question":"Why don\u0027t we try 300 million?","answer":"Well, you see, you want to confiscate all guns in the United States.","docId":"121203pmt","qSentId":104,"aSentId":105},{"question":"What is your take on it?","answer":"It\u0027s mind-boggling to me.","docId":"121203pmt","qSentId":178,"aSentId":179},{"question":"What is your view of what he said and his right to say it?","answer":"Well, again, there\u0027s a time and a place.","docId":"121203pmt","qSentId":197,"aSentId":198},{"question":"Short of bringing you out of retirement, what should they be doing?","answer":"Well, they ought to be dealing with this on the up-and-up instead of dealing the way they are.","docId":"121203pmt","qSentId":215,"aSentId":216},{"question":"Confident?","answer":"Now you\u0027re talking about some good football there, buddy.","docId":"121203pmt","qSentId":227,"aSentId":228},{"question":"The law is being changed to ensure that whoever the firstborn child is, boy or girl, will automatically become king or queen, but it\u0027s not actually a done deal yet, is it?","answer":"No, it\u0027s not.","docId":"121203pmt","qSentId":272,"aSentId":273},{"question":"Is it literally the first one out is the heir?","answer":"Well, like you say, if this legislation comes into play, which I suspect it will ahead of the birth, then yes, if the firstborn, the first twin to birth is a girl, then she will take precedence over either the sister or the brother.","docId":"121203pmt","qSentId":284,"aSentId":285},{"question":"People call it acute morning sickness or whatever, but it\u0027s a bit worse than that, isn\u0027t it?","answer":"It is worse than just typical morning sickness.","docId":"121203pmt","qSentId":306,"aSentId":307},{"question":"Does it increase the potential risk of a miscarriage?","answer":"Well, it does increase the possible risk of having a baby prematurely, although if you look across the board, most babies are born perfectly healthy so it\u0027s a small increase in that sort of condition but typically if it\u0027s going to be treated well and again, lasting just a few weeks, then everything should go pretty well after that.","docId":"121203pmt","qSentId":319,"aSentId":320},{"question":"And do you see again -- I know you\u0027ve done so much on this, but do you see a potential parallel here with him?","answer":"Well, you know, I think a lot of people are certainly looking that way.","docId":"121203pmt","qSentId":324,"aSentId":325},{"question":"Given that both sides know where they need to move, why the games?","answer":"Well, it\u0027s not clear that both sides know.","docId":"121203pmt","qSentId":363,"aSentId":364},{"question":"You\u0027re calling Reid as well?","answer":"Oh, yes, absolutely.","docId":"121203pmt","qSentId":444,"aSentId":445},{"question":"How did you feel?","answer":"Standing on the stage at the White House looking out at my buddies that I served in combat with, all the brass in the military, two families that had lost their sons that night that I was being awarded this medal for, it was very bittersweet.","docId":"121203pmt","qSentId":478,"aSentId":479},{"question":"What is your view about gun control in America?","answer":"I absolutely love the Second Amendment.","docId":"121203pmt","qSentId":548,"aSentId":549},{"question":"What is life going to be like for you now?","answer":"Life\u0027s exciting.","docId":"121203pmt","qSentId":557,"aSentId":558}]